fr.sorbonne_u.cps.smartcity.components

Class SAMUStationProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sorbonne_u.components.AbstractComponent
      • fr.sorbonne_u.cps.smartcity.components.SAMUStationProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    fr.sorbonne_u.components.ComponentI, SAMUActionImplI

    public class SAMUStationProxy
extends fr.sorbonne_u.components.AbstractComponent
implements SAMUActionImplI
    The class SAMUStationProxy implements a SAMU station for the basic simulator, which is meant to simply test all of the possible notifications sent by a SAMU station and all of the possible actions that a SAMU station can execute, without doing anything per se but rather act as a test plug-in.

    Description

    Invariant

     invariant      true

    Created on : 2022-02-04
